=== 巴素利 ===
2008年1月[[圖恩足球俱樂部|杜安]]借用貝美亞六個月，季後返回巴素利，與主教練[[Christian_Gross|格羅斯]]（Christian Gross）商討後，於7月13日巴素利宣布回購貝美亞最後一年的合約，讓他可以自由身加盟其他球隊<small><ref>FC Basel website：[http://www.fcb.ch/news/show/byItemID//10044/20450/16/7 {{de}} Vertrag FCB-Franz Burgmeier beendet] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080812072721/http://www.fcb.ch/news/show/byItemID/10044/20450/16/7 |date=2008-08-12 }}</ref></small>

=== 達寧頓 ===
貝美亞獲得其他瑞士球隊及剛降級[[法乙|法乙]]的[[梅斯足球俱乐部|梅斯]]招手，但[[达灵顿足球俱乐部|達寧頓]]於2008年8月21日獲得貝美亞加盟<small><ref>The Northern Echo：[http://www.thenorthernecho.co.uk/sport/football/darlington/3612399.Quakers_sign_international_winger/ {{Wayback|url=http://www.thenorthernecho.co.uk/sport/football/darlington/3612399.Quakers_sign_international_winger/ |date=20160304122926 }} {{Wayback|url=http://www.thenorthernecho.co.uk/sport/football/darlington/3612399.Quakers_sign_international_winger/ |date=20160304122926 }} {{Wayback|url=http://www.thenorthernecho.co.uk/sport/football/darlington/3612399.Quakers_sign_international_winger/ |date=20160304122926 }} {{Wayback|url=http://www.thenorthernecho.co.uk/sport/football/darlington/3612399.Quakers_sign_international_winger/ |date=20160304122926 }} {{en}} Quakers sign international winger]</ref></small><small><ref>BBC Sport：[http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/d/darlington/7575271.stm {{Wayback|url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/d/darlington/7575271.stm |date=20080822065635 }} {{Wayback|url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/d/darlington/7575271.stm |date=20080822065635 }} {{Wayback|url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/d/darlington/7575271.stm |date=20080822065635 }} {{Wayback|url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/d/darlington/7575271.stm |date=20080822065635 }} {{en}} Quakers sign Liechtenstein star]</ref></small>。8月23日即首次代表達寧頓主場出戰[[吉林汉姆足球俱乐部|基寧咸]]，以1-2敗陣。9月13日主場對[[韦尔港足球俱乐部|維爾港]]的2-1勝仗中取得首個聯賽入球<small><ref>BBC Sport：[http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_div_3/7602065.stm {{Wayback|url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_div_3/7602065.stm |date=20080917192727 }} {{Wayback|url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_div_3/7602065.stm |date=20080917192727 }} {{Wayback|url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_div_3/7602065.stm |date=20080917192727 }} {{Wayback|url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_div_3/7602065.stm |date=20080917192727 }} {{en}} Darlington 2-1 Port Vale]</ref></small>。基寧咸嚴重財困而需要進行財務重組，由於未有新買家接手，於2008/09年球季後清洗主力陣容，貝美亞返回家鄉加盟[[瓦杜茲足球俱樂部|華杜茲]]。

